\id 2TI - Akawaio New Testament Translation Project
\h 2 TEMU'TI
\toc1 Iyakon Ite'kwaro' Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ Temu'ti Ena'
\toc2 2 Temu'ti
\toc3 2 Temu'ti
\mt2 Iyakon Ite'kwaro' Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ
\mt1 Temu'ti
\mt2 Ena'
\imt1 Ekamanin
\ip \bk Iyakon Ite'kwaro' Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ Temu'ti Ena'\bk* esi eke pe kuru ipoi rɨ Temu'ti panamato' en pe, moine pe, tisakon pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉpika'tɨnin pe iyesi pɨ'. Isauro'to' ipɨ' esi, imoronkato'. Temu'ti panamasa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipori'mapɨ'sa' esi tʉni'tunʉ Sises Kʉrai ekareei ekamato' pe iya iye'to' awɨrɨ, ita'sito' pe i'nairon wakʉ itekare pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ penaro' ekonekan nʉ'pʉ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ti'sa pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itekare ekamanin pe te'to' tʉrawasooi ku'to' pe iya, tʉkota'ma mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tewa'noma annawɨrɨ rɨ.
\ip Temu'ti kuru panamasa' mɨrɨ, “Se pe rɨ i'tui'ma pʉra rɨ e'sei'pɨ'nɨto' yau e'nɨto' pɨ'” (2:23). Wakʉ ku'nin pen nɨ, e'tane ka'pon etanin ma'tanʉ'nin nɨ.
\ip Tanporo serɨ yau, Temu'ti emiya'pontɨpɨtʉ imenukanin nʉ'pʉ uko'manto' pɨ', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ mɨrɨ to' pe rɨ iye'to' pɨ'—apurɨto' iya, iseta'kato' pen, isi'nʉnkato', imoronkato' iya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ e'ne' moronkato' iya tʉkota'mato' yau.
\iot Iyawon Ekamanin
\io1 Ekamanin (1:1-2)
\io1 Apurɨpɨtʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pana' pe ipanama (1:3—2:13)
\io1 Panaman (2:14—4:5)
\io1 Paarʉ rɨ nin si e'to' eseru (4:6-18)
\io1 Iu'matʉ (4:19-22)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Paarʉ, Kʉrai Sises nennoko'pʉ Papa eseru winɨ, ikupʉ uya tukai' usauro'nɨsa' rʉ'pʉ uko'man nɨto' pɨ' awɨrɨ Kʉrai Sises yau na'ne' winɨpaino,
\p 
\v 2 Temu'ti, umu rʉ'kwɨ enakan:\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 16:1\x*
\p Wakʉ nonkasa', usentu'man nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' Papa, Ikʉipʉnʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kʉrai Sises, Uyepuru kon winon nesii ɨiwano' kon pe.
\s1 Pori'mapɨ' Nɨto' Iyawɨron Pe
\p 
\v 3 Tenki ta uya Papa iyapiyo' pe esii'ma unapurɨpɨtʉnʉ pɨ', utamokori ton uya ikuu'pʉ kasa, wakʉ pe itewan esii'ma ewarupɨ kaisa rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wʉi kaisa rɨ inke rɨ uyenu yau ɨkupʉ uya ɨpʉrema yau.
\v 4 Aukaramʉ'pʉ senuminkapɨ'ai', ipan pe ɨyenpai kanan e'ai', ipan pe pori' pe e'to' pe.
\v 5 Uyemiya'pontɨsa' man i'nai rɨ apurɨto' auya pɨ', wapiya iko'mansa' ɨno' Ʉrowis mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ asan Yunes yau, mɨrɨpan nɨ esi ayau uko'man nɨ pɨ' rɨ marɨ tukai' kuru i'tu uya.\x - \xo 1:5 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 16:1\x*
\v 6 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', ɨyemiya'pontɨ uya Papa uya ɨrepato' ike iwouwoumakɨ iye'peukato' pe, ayau na'ne' uyemiya nonka uya ɨpona winɨ.
\v 7 Apʉne pʉra Papa uya enari'ke' a'kwarʉ wannɨ ke repan nɨsa' pen, e'tane meruntɨ a'kwarʉ wannɨ ke, tʉusi'nʉnkasen mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tiwa rɨ tepanamasen.
\p 
\v 8 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', kɨpiyɨtʉi uyepuru kon ekama auya pɨ', mɨrɨ pe pʉra urɨ pɨ' ipɨkɨrɨ a'sisa' pe na'ne'. E'tane upokon pe e'nɨpai ekota'man yau itekare wenai, Papa meruntɨrʉ winɨ,
\v 9 upika'tɨnin nʉ'pʉ kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ukɨ'manin nʉ'pʉ kon wakʉ pe uko'man nɨto' ya'—ɨ'rɨ ku'sa' wenai pen e'tane iku'to' pe tiwano' pe rɨ inkuu'pʉ rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ nonkasa'. Serɨ wakʉ nonkasa' e'tʉrʉ'pʉ Kʉrai Sises yau pata weyu epiya'tɨ rawɨrɨ,
\v 10 e'tane serɨ pe si isenpoikasa' upika'tɨnin kon Kʉrai Sises usenpoika poro, uma'tan nɨto' ma'tanʉ'nin nʉ'pʉ, mɨrɨpan uya teri'se pʉra uko'man nɨto' ne'sa' tensen pe itekare awɨrɨ.
\v 11 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ serɨ itekare anin pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ enno'sa' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ti'sa pe anʉnsa' urɨ.\x - \xo 1:11 \xt 1 Temu'ti 2:7\x*
\v 12 Mɨrɨ wenai ekota'ma e'ai'ne' kasa. Mɨrɨ e'tane ɨpiyɨtʉ pen, apʉne pʉra i'tu uya unapurɨ'pʉ, mɨrɨpan esi tena' unnonka'pʉ\f + \fr 1:12 \fq tena' unnonka'pʉ; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq uyena' innonka'pʉ\f* mɨrɨ Itepuru uyepʉ weyu a'taino erasu pe tukai' i'tu uya.
\p 
\v 13 Ɨneta'pʉ uwinɨ iku'kɨ wakʉ enupan nɨto' ento' ipɨ' pe, apurɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ usi'nʉnkan nɨto' pokon pe Kʉrai Sises yau.
\v 14 Ɨyena' inonkasa' na'ne' wakʉ itʉsa' erasu pe e'kɨ—iterasu pe e'kɨ Wakʉ A'kwarʉ uya tʉpika'tɨi' uyau'nokon nʉko'manyai'ne'.
\p 
\v 15 I'tu auya tanporon kon nɨ Eisa nono pon kon uya unonkasa', Paikeras mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Ɨmosines pokon uya rɨ.
\p 
\v 16 Tɨwɨ Itepuru nʉsentu'mai Oni'si'poros iwʉ' tawon kon pɨ', apʉne pʉra inke rʉ'kwɨ rɨ uya'kwarʉ ne'pɨ'nin pe iyesi pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ urɨ i'sen pɨ' iyɨpiyɨ'sa' pʉra iyesi pɨ'.
\v 17 Mɨrɨ kasa pʉra, Ron po tesi a'tai, sa'man pe rɨ uwarinpa pɨ' iyesi'pʉ uyeporo tʉuya pona rɨ.
\v 18 Tɨwɨ Itepuru nʉkupʉi Itepuru winon usentu'man nɨto' eponin pe Itepuru weyu a'tai! I'tu auya rɨ wakʉ pe, eke pe rɨ upika'tɨ'pʉ iya E'pe'sas po esi a'tai.
\c 2
\s1 Sa'man Annau Rɨ Temu'ti E'to'
\p 
\v 1 Ɨmɨrɨ nin si, umu, pana' pe e'kɨ wakʉ nonkasa' yau Kʉrai Sises yau na'ne'.
\v 2 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ mɨ ton tu'kan kon ennin nʉ'san koro'tau ta uya metataine' itʉkɨ wakʉ pe iku'nin nan ka'pon amʉ' ena' to' usenupasa' e'to' pe tʉron kon kanan enupanin nan pe.
\v 3 Sa'man pe rɨ te'sen imoronkakɨ ina pokon pe Kʉrai Sises soisaai wakʉ ye' pe.
\v 4 Ɨnʉ' rɨ soisa pe te'sen uya soisa pe pʉra e'nɨ tʉrawasooi kupʉ pʉra iyesi, apʉne pʉra tanʉnnin nʉ'pʉ ɨnpori'mapai tesi wenai.
\v 5 Mɨrɨ kasa rɨ kanan, ka'pon teka'tunsen tʉron kon a'kɨrɨ uya tepe'pʉ aro', kʉron eporo pʉra iyesi, eporo iya rɨ nin iteseru awɨrɨ iyeka'tunsa' a'tai.
\v 6 Sa'man pe te'tʉrawasomai' temaina'tɨsen uya kuru wapiya tepe'pʉ epoto' pe iyesi umɨ apai.
\v 7 Serɨ ukayai'ne' pɨ' ɨsenuminkakɨ, apʉne pʉra Itepuru uya ɨpika'tɨ mɨrɨ tanporo serɨ ton to'ka'nʉkʉ pa.
\p 
\v 8 Ɨyenu yau Sises Kʉrai iku'kɨ, iye'mʉ'sa'kasa' rʉ'pʉ terikʉ'pʉ yapai, Tepi' awonsi'kɨ iu'tɨsa' rʉ'pʉ. Serɨ serɨ uyekareei,
\v 9 mɨrɨ wenai ekota'ma auronpɨ'sa' pe rɨ i'sen ke ɨri ku'nin nʉ'pʉ kasa rɨ. E'tane Papa maimu esi auronpɨ'sa' i'sen ke pe pʉra rɨ.
\v 10 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ' tanporon nɨ moronka uya anʉnsa' kon iwano' pe, to' uya nɨrɨ epika'tɨn nɨto' epoto' pe Kʉrai Sises yau na'ne', tɨwɨro' rɨ a'kwa pokon pe.
\p 
\v 11 Serɨ serɨ tapurɨsen kuru main:
\q1 Kʉrai pokon pe eri'nɨsa' yau,
\q2 ipokon pe rɨ kanan uko'man nɨ;
\q1 
\v 12 Imoronkasa' pe iyesi yau,\x - \xo 2:12 \xt Ma'siu 10:33; Ʉru' 12:9\x*
\q2 ipokon pe rɨ marɨ itepuru pe rɨ marɨ e'nɨto' oton;
\q1 Inonkasa' pe iyesi yau,
\q2 unonka iya 'nokon nɨ nɨrɨ;
\q1 
\v 13 Imaimu awɨrɨ pʉra e'nɨ yau,
\q2 uyauro'ka'pʉ tʉuya 'nokon awɨrɨ rɨ nin iyesi,
\q2 apʉne pʉra tʉusaurokʉ'pʉ pu'tɨka'nʉ'nin pe pʉra tesi pɨ'.
\s1 Tʉrawaso Ye' Wakʉ Tato' Papa Uya Ipɨ'
\p 
\v 14 To' emiya'pontɨpɨ' rɨ e'kɨ serɨ ton pɨ'. To' ipanamakɨ Papa rau, main ton wenai rɨ ɨsipɨ' e'nɨ pɨ' to' esi namai'; se pe rɨ iyesi, mɨrɨpan esi etapɨ' te'san ma'tanʉ'nin pe rɨ.
\v 15 Wakʉ pe kuru e'kɨ Papa ena' ɨye'tʉrʉ pa wakʉ tato' iya ipɨ' pe, tʉrawaso ye' tɨpiyɨ'sen pen mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipoken kuru i'nairon maimu anin ye' pe.
\v 16 Papa uya tasa' pen nɨ pɨ' usauro'nɨto' yau kesii, apʉne pʉra kamo iyau te'san ena mɨrɨ miyarɨ rɨ Papa uya tasa' pen nɨ awɨrɨ.
\v 17 Enupan nɨto' to' uya ike e'ta'nʉkʉ mɨrɨ werei e'to' kasa. To' koro'tawon kon man Aimeniyas mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Pairi'tas,
\v 18 i'nairon piyapai itɨsa' kon. E'mʉ'sa'kan nɨto' oton tato' e'ku'ka'sa' rɨ ta to' uya, mɨrɨpan kon uya tʉron kon uya apurɨto' ma'tanʉkʉ.
\v 19 Mɨrɨ rɨ e'tane, Papa iwano' sa'man nɨ iyapon esi pana' pe rɨ iye'mʉ'sa'kasa' pe, se tawon ke ipɨ' a'si'sa': “Itepuru uya to' i'tu kamoro tiwano' pe te'san,”\f + \fr 2:19 \ft Nonpa 16:5 (LXX)\f* mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ, “Tanporon kon Itepuru ese' ekamayai'ne' nan nera'tɨi ɨri pe e'nɨto' apai,” tawon ke.
\p 
\v 20 Eke ɨutɨ tau moro apuru ton esi korʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ sirʉpa pun konekasa' rɨken pen, e'tane yʉi mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨinɨ pun; tʉron nɨ ton esi eke ɨ'rɨ rɨ e'kupʉ a'taino pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉron nɨ ton se pan nɨ nin ku'to' a'taino pe.
\v 21 Serɨ iwa pe na'ne' ɨri ton sepa' nan yapai ka'pon ekorʉka yau, eke kupʉ a'taino iku'to' ike ye' pe, wakʉ pe iyekonekasa' pe, tesa' napurɨnʉ ye' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ti'tui' pʉra rɨ wakʉ tʉrawaso ku'nin pe iyesi mɨrɨ.
\p 
\v 22 Ainʉnkɨ ɨri moine ton e'to' i'se piyapai, mɨrɨpan ipoken e'nɨto', apurɨto', usi'nʉnkan nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' ku'nin pe ɨwesi pa, kamo Itepuru esakʉ pɨ' na'ne' nan wakʉ pe itewan esii'ma pokon pe.
\v 23 Iya'kwarʉ pʉra rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ se pe rɨ e'sei'pɨ' nɨto' kʉsa'pɨ'pɨtʉi, apʉne pʉra i'tu auya ɨsipɨ' e'nɨto' emapu'tɨ iya.
\v 24 Mɨrɨpan Itepuru poitorʉ e'to' pe pʉra iyesi ɨsipɨ'; e'tane ru'ku, mannʉ' pe iye'to' pe iyesi tanporon kon pɨ', enupanin pe, tʉpɨ' e'nɨto' anʉnnin pe pʉra e'ne' pe.
\v 25 Kamo tewa'nomanin nan enupato' iya pe iyesi ɨ'sɨ'mʉn yai, e'kupʉi'ma Papa uya to' kupʉ tera'tɨsen pe to' anin pe i'nairon i'tuto' ya',
\v 26 mɨrɨpan kon a'kwarʉ uye'to' pe mɨrɨpan kon ainʉnto' pe Makoi mareei apai, to' a'sisa' iya na'ne' i'se te'to' ku'nin pe.
\c 3
\s1 Papa Uya Tasa' Pen Nɨ Awɨrɨ E'nɨ Pata Weyu U'matʉ Yau
\p 
\v 1 E'tane serɨ nesii ɨyenu yau: Moro ɨsɨ rɨ e'to' oton mɨrɨ pata weyu u'matʉ yau.
\v 2 Tʉmɨrɨ'nokon pe ka'pon amʉ' usi'nʉnkato' oton, pʉrata i'nʉnkanin nan pe, tʉutapurɨsan pe, mɨ pe e'ku'nɨ pɨ', e'sapeman pɨ', tʉsan kon maimu awɨrɨ pʉra e'nɨ pɨ', tenki tawon pe pʉra, Papa namanin pe pʉra,
\v 3 usi'nʉnkan nɨto' pʉra, tʉusentu'masen pe pʉra, ɨri pe tʉron kon pɨ' tʉusauro'san pe, tiwano' kon pe tʉuse'se'tɨi' te'san pe pʉra, ɨsɨ ton pe rɨ, wakʉ i'nʉnkanin nan pe pʉra rɨ,
\v 4 eparankanin nan tonpa pe e'kupʉi'ma, inke pʉra rɨ ɨri ku'nin nan pe, ipan pe mɨ pe te'ku'san pe, tʉpori'manin kon i'nʉnkanin nan pe Papa i'nʉnka pe ekama tane—
\v 5 Papa uya tasa' pɨ' tesi kon tukai' to' e'kupʉ e'tane imeruntɨrʉ nurunpa to' uya. To' kʉsa'pɨ'pɨtʉi.
\p 
\v 6 Mɨrɨ waraino kon pe to' esi, iwʉ' wannɨ ta' ama'ai tewonsan pe mɨrɨpan kon uya iya'kwarʉ pʉnon kon uri'sami'si amʉ' a'si, makoi ke tʉuse'tape'mai' te'san ti'tui' pʉra rɨ ɨri ton to' e'to' i'se nʉpininpanʉ ton,
\v 7 tɨwɨrɨ rɨ tʉusenupasan e'tane i'nairon i'tu pokena' ton pen nɨ.
\v 8 Isanes mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Isanpʉres\f + \fr 3:8 \fq Isanes mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Isanpʉres\ft —Serɨ ese' ton e'seporo pʉra iyesi mɨrɨ Penaro' Ekonekan nɨto' yau, e'tane tu'kan kon uya apurɨ serɨ ese' ton esi'pʉ asa'ron kon Isi' pon kon enwoke' ton Mosi' ewa'nomanin nʉ'san Esuwerʉ amʉ' arɨ i'se iyesi a'tai Isi' yapai. Apʉne E'sotas 7:11-22 enkɨ.\f* uya Mosi' ewa'noma'pʉ kasa kuru, mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ pʉsamoro ka'pon amʉ' uya i'nairon ewa'noma—ka'pon amʉ' isenuminkato' ima'tasa' kon, apurɨto' pɨ' e'nɨ koro'tau, eno'masa' kon nɨ.\x - \xo 3:8 \xt Isi'kiyerʉ 7:11\x*
\v 9 E'tane inke to' esi pen nɨ mɨrɨ apʉne pʉra iya'kwarʉ pʉra to' e'to' esi tense.
\s1 Temu'ti Apiyontɨ Paarʉ Uya
\p 
\v 10 E'tane, ɨmɨrɨ nin si, ɨmɨrɨ uya tanporo enupan nɨto' uya i'tu, uko'mamʉ eseru, ɨ'rɨ ku'nin pe e'to, apurɨto', tʉuseta'kai' pʉra e'to', usi'nʉnkato', imoronkato',
\v 11 ukota'mato', e'ne' moronkato' uya—ti'tui' pʉra rɨ iye'ku'sa' rʉ'pʉ upɨ' Antiyo', Ai'koniyan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Restʉra po, ukota'mato' moronka'pʉ uya. Mɨrɨ rɨ e'tane Itepuru uya umo'ka'pʉ tanporo mɨrɨ ton apai.\x - \xo 3:11 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 13:14-52; 14:1-7, 8-20\x*
\v 12 I'nai rɨ sa'ne, tanporon kon Papa uya tasa' kasa ɨko'manpaino kon Kʉrai Sises yau kota'mato' pe iyesi,
\v 13 ɨri ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ enku'tɨnin nan utɨ tane miyarɨ rɨ enku'tɨn pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ usenku'tɨn pɨ'.
\v 14 E'tane ɨmɨrɨ nin tɨ, ɨusenupa'pʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'nai rɨ anapurɨ'pʉ yawɨrɨ rɨ ɨko'mankɨ, apʉne pʉra to' i'tu auya kamoro iwinɨ ipɨ' ɨusenupa'pʉ ton,
\v 15 mɨrɨpan mʉre pe ɨwesi'pʉ si'kɨrɨ imenukasa' wakʉ itekare ton i'tu auya, ta'kwarʉ ke ɨku'nin epika'tɨn nɨto' pɨ' Kʉrai Sises apurɨto' auya poro.
\v 16 Tanporon imenukasa' itekare esi Papa nʉkuu'pʉ pe Ta'kwarʉ winɨ, enupan nɨto' ike pe, esereme'to' ike, isuraikato' ike, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ enupan nɨto' ipokena' pe tʉuko'mansen pe,
\v 17 Papa poitorʉ pe te'sen utapuruui'tɨto' pe wakʉ pe kuru tanporon wakʉ tʉrawaso iwano' pe.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Papa mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kʉrai Sises uya entane, nurɨnan kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iyeri'sa' kon aimenka ton, isenpoikato' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ esa' wannɨ pe iye'to' pɨ' tense, ɨrepa uya serɨ utapiyontɨn nɨto' ke:
\v 2 Itekare ekama'; ekonekakɨ iweyu a'taino pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iweyu a'taino pe pʉra rɨ; to' isuraika', to' esereme'kɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' ipori'makɨ—tʉuseta'kai' pʉra kuru mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ti'tui' kuru to' nʉkupʉnʉ ke to' enupa'.
\v 3 Apʉne pʉra iweyu uye'to' oton ka'pon amʉ' uya wakʉ usenupan nɨto' etato' oton pen. E'tane ru'ku, i'se te'to' kon ɨnetapai to' e'to' oton, tu'ke kuru ti'sa amʉ' amʉranʉ'to' oton to' uya tʉpana kon e'si'si'mato' ɨnetapai ekamanin pe.
\v 4 Tʉpana kon ra'tɨ to' uya i'nairon piyapai, mɨrɨpan kon era'tɨ i'nairon pen panton winɨkʉi'.
\v 5 E'tane ɨmɨrɨ, tanporon yau rɨ ti'tui' e'kɨ, sa'man moronkanin pe, itekare ekamanin tʉrawasooi iku'kɨ, tanporo ɨnkupʉnʉ ɨtʉrawasooi iku'ka'kɨ.
\p 
\v 6 Apʉne pʉra iu'matʉ pe umaka'sa' man use'man nɨto' ike tensisen kasa, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ utɨto' weyu si e'sepoka'sa'.
\v 7 Eto'sa' rɨ man wakʉ pɨ' eto'nɨto' yau, eka'tunto' i'ma'kasa' uya man, apurɨto' awɨrɨ rɨ e'sa' man.
\v 8 Serɨ nin si ipoken e'nɨto' arʉkooi, kʉron esi moro, Itepuru, ipokena' eseru Aimenkanin uya uye'mato' oton ike mɨrɨ wʉi a'tai—urɨ rɨken pen, e'tane tanporon kon nɨ nɨrɨ isenpoika enupɨkɨrɨ iye'sa' kon.
\s1 Tʉpɨ' Rɨ Isauro'to'
\p 
\v 9 Inke pʉra parɨ upiya' ɨsi'kɨ,
\v 10 apʉne pʉra Temas uya unonkasa' man, mɨrɨpan utɨ'pʉ man Tesaroni'ka pona, serɨ orʉ i'nʉnka tʉuya pɨ'. Kʉre'sin utɨ'pʉ man Kare'siya pona, Tai'tas nɨrɨ utɨ'pʉ Tarʉma'siya pona.\x - \xo 4:10 \xt Koro'se 4:14; Pairiman 24; 2 Koren 8:23; Kare'siya 2:3; Tai'tas 1:4\x*
\v 11 Ʉru' rɨken man upiyau. Ɨuyepʉ a'tai, Ma' tepose ine'kɨ aya'kɨrɨ, apʉne pʉra upika'tɨnin pe i'se esi pɨ' utʉrawasooi yau.\x - \xo 4:11 \xt Koro'se 4:14; Pairiman 24; Inkupʉ'pʉ 12:12, 25; 13:13; 15:37-39; Koro'se 4:10\x*
\v 12 Tai'ki'kas nin ennoko'pʉ uya man E'pe'sas pona.\x - \xo 4:12 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 20:4; E'pe'sas 6:21-22; Koro'se 4:7-8\x*
\v 13 Ɨuyepʉ a'tai, upon pʉro'pon mʉnepʉi' unnɨmɨ'pʉ Tʉrowas po Karʉ'pas piyau, ukaretaai amon ton nɨrɨ, o' pi'pɨ konekasa' ton kuru, mʉnepʉi'.\x - \xo 4:13 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 20:6\x*
\p 
\v 14 Tinin konekanin Arisanta uya ekamʉra uku'sa' man; Itepuru uya rɨ e'ma mɨrɨ, mɨrɨ kupʉ'pʉ iya epe'pʉ pe.\x - \xo 4:14 \xt 1 Temu'ti 1:20; Eren 62:12; Ron 2:6\x*
\v 15 Ɨmɨrɨ rɨ nɨrɨ, enei'ma rɨ nɨrɨ mesii', ekamʉra ɨkupʉ iya namai', apʉne pʉra ina nekamanʉ itekare ewaruma'tɨ iya pɨ' ipan pe rɨ.
\p 
\v 16 Wapiyaro' kasi pe upɨ' usauro'nɨto' ekama uya a'tai, ɨnʉ' uyee'pʉ pen nɨ upika'tɨi'; e'tane tanporon kon uya rɨ unonkasa' esi'pʉ. Papa uya to' kota'ma i'se pʉra e'ai' mɨrɨ wenai.
\v 17 E'tane Itepuru esi'pʉ upiyau mɨrɨpan uya umeruntɨtanʉkʉ'pʉ, uporo itekare usekamaka'to' pe tanporo mɨrɨpan tanporo Esuwerʉ ton pen uya etaka'to' pe. Rayan mʉta apai nin si emo'ka'pʉ mɨrɨ.
\v 18 Itepuru uya rɨ umo'ka mɨrɨ tanporon nɨ ɨri uya uyeparantɨto' apai, mɨrɨpan uya wakʉ pe uyenpa'ka Epʉn po esa' wannɨ pe te'to' ya'. Itenakan pe eke pe iku'to' nesii tɨwɨrɨ rɨ. Amen.
\s1 Iu'matʉ Pe Miyarɨ Tato'
\p 
\v 19 Miyarɨ ka'kɨ Pʉre'sira\f + \fr 4:19 \ft Kiri' pe \fq Pʉri'sa, Pʉre'sira \ft pɨ' rɨ tʉron nɨ pe\f* mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ A'kira pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Oni'si'poros iwʉ' tawon kon pɨ'.\x - \xo 4:19 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 18:2; 2 Temu'ti 1:16-17\x*
\v 20 Erastas e'nɨmɨ'pʉ Koren po, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ takuru' ke Tʉro'pimas sinɨntai Mairi'tos po.\x - \xo 4:20 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 19:22; Ron 16:23; Inkupʉ'pʉ 20:4; 21:29\x*
\v 21 Komi' pe pata esi weyu rawɨrɨ parɨ ɨsi'kɨ serɨ ya'. Iupiyoros, Piyutens, Rainos, Kʉratiya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporo utonpa kon amʉ' rɨ nɨrɨ miyarɨ ta pɨ' man ɨpɨ'.
\v 22 Itepuru nesii aya'kwarʉ a'kɨrɨ. Wakʉ nonkasa' nesii ɨpiyau'nokon.
